1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:12,000
(Watch on www.kisskh.li Support Admin)

2
00:00:37,180 --> 00:00:40,300
(Press Conference)

3
00:00:40,300 --> 00:00:41,500
Good afternoon.

4
00:00:41,940 --> 00:00:43,220
I am Xu Wanxin.

5
00:00:43,900 --> 00:00:44,859
Today,

6
00:00:44,860 --> 00:00:46,979
in my capacity
as Interim Chairwoman of Minghui Group,

7
00:00:46,980 --> 00:00:49,060
I am here to announce
important decisions of the Group.

8
00:00:49,100 --> 00:00:50,220
First,

9
00:00:50,340 --> 00:00:53,820
the remains of Mr. Xu Zhaoming,
former President of Minghui Group,

10
00:00:53,980 --> 00:00:55,820
have been safely returned to Gang City.

11
00:00:57,540 --> 00:00:59,060
The funeral will be held tomorrow.

12
00:00:59,140 --> 00:01:01,320
We ask that members of the media
refrain from disturbance.

13
00:01:03,100 --> 00:01:04,220
Second,

14
00:01:04,340 --> 00:01:06,059
Chairman Xu Qianmo

15
00:01:06,060 --> 00:01:07,740
is currently in stable condition.

16
00:01:08,900 --> 00:01:11,020
We appreciate the attention
and concern from all sectors.

17
00:01:11,500 --> 00:01:12,899
Although Minghui

18
00:01:12,900 --> 00:01:15,620
is presently facing
significant turbulence and challenges,

19
00:01:16,500 --> 00:01:18,020
up to this point,

20
00:01:18,380 --> 00:01:20,299
our cooperation with Junlin Group

21
00:01:20,300 --> 00:01:22,740
continues to progress
steadily and intensively.

22
00:01:23,820 --> 00:01:25,820
Now, please welcome my fiance,

23
00:01:27,180 --> 00:01:31,100
Mr. Shen Gu, shareholder
of Junlin Group, to speak.

24
00:01:41,700 --> 00:01:44,060
Ladies and gentlemen, good afternoon.

25
00:01:44,300 --> 00:01:45,540
I am Shen Gu.

26
00:01:46,300 --> 00:01:47,740
It is a great honor

27
00:01:47,980 --> 00:01:50,459
to stand here

28
00:01:50,460 --> 00:01:51,860
as Miss Xu Wanxin's fiance.

29
00:01:52,900 --> 00:01:56,140
I am truly grateful to Miss Xu Wanxin

30
00:01:56,500 --> 00:02:00,060
for choosing me in this partnership
between Junlin and Minghui.

31
00:02:00,300 --> 00:02:01,379
From this day forward,

32
00:02:01,380 --> 00:02:03,139
I will uphold Minghui Group's

33
00:02:03,140 --> 00:02:05,620
century-long founding vision.

34
00:02:05,740 --> 00:02:07,120
(Junlin Group)
Creating value for the people,

35
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:08,760
contributing to the prosperity
of the nation.

36
00:02:08,980 --> 00:02:10,100
Finally,

37
00:02:10,460 --> 00:02:12,820
as the largest shareholder
of Junlin Group,

38
00:02:13,020 --> 00:02:15,499
I will commit thirty-five percent
of my shares

39
00:02:15,500 --> 00:02:18,540
to ensure the stability of cooperation
between the two companies.

40
00:02:18,740 --> 00:02:20,660
Quite an honor?

41
00:02:21,580 --> 00:02:23,220
You really played the part well.

42
00:02:23,620 --> 00:02:25,099
Anyone watching would think

43
00:02:25,100 --> 00:02:27,540
you were the one
engaged to Xu Wanxin for eight years.

44
00:02:28,620 --> 00:02:30,139
Can you keep your composure?

45
00:02:30,140 --> 00:02:32,660
At this rate, how will you
ever achieve anything big?

46
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:42,739
Dump all the Minghui shares
in your hands.

47
00:02:42,740 --> 00:02:44,699
I want Minghui stock

48
00:02:44,700 --> 00:02:47,179
to drop below 120 today.

49
00:02:47,180 --> 00:02:48,540
Yes.

50
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:52,439
=Echoes of Gang City=

51
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:57,239
=Episode 4=
(Very convincing)

52
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:59,840
(Minghui Holdings)

53
00:03:03,300 --> 00:03:05,380
Shen Tingyuan's people
have already begun to act.

54
00:03:06,260 --> 00:03:07,380
No need to rush.

55
00:03:08,860 --> 00:03:10,059
What Shen Tingyuan is doing

56
00:03:10,060 --> 00:03:12,420
is sending a signal to the market.

57
00:03:13,060 --> 00:03:16,100
Shen Gu does not represent Junlin Group.

58
00:03:16,100 --> 00:03:18,259
Could it be that in the end
we will really be pushed by Datong Bank

59
00:03:18,260 --> 00:03:20,460
into early loan repayment?

60
00:03:22,340 --> 00:03:23,099
Miss Xu,

61
00:03:23,100 --> 00:03:24,619
Minghui Group's stock is dropping.

62
00:03:24,620 --> 00:03:27,100
Do you have any measures
to stabilize the share price?

63
00:03:32,260 --> 00:03:35,620
Thank you to all members of the media
for your attention and support for our Group.

64
00:03:36,100 --> 00:03:36,619
As for this...

65
00:03:36,620 --> 00:03:37,339
Minghui!

66
00:03:37,340 --> 00:03:38,260
Watch out!

67
00:04:01,160 --> 00:04:04,200
(Minghui Group Press Conference)

68
00:04:11,860 --> 00:04:12,939
Minghui,

69
00:04:12,940 --> 00:04:14,860
return our hard-earned money!

70
00:04:14,940 --> 00:04:15,859
Minghui,

71
00:04:15,860 --> 00:04:17,979
return our hard-earned money!

72
00:04:17,980 --> 00:04:19,100
Take him away!

73
00:04:19,700 --> 00:04:20,820
What was that just thrown?

74
00:04:21,580 --> 00:04:22,700
It smells awful.

75
00:04:22,860 --> 00:04:23,979
Dear members of the press,

76
00:04:23,980 --> 00:04:24,939
it is ammonia.

77
00:04:24,940 --> 00:04:27,100
The concentration is low.
Please remain calm.

78
00:04:27,900 --> 00:04:29,420
Are you alright?

79
00:04:39,940 --> 00:04:41,340
Are you hurt?

80
00:04:42,140 --> 00:04:43,260
I'm fine.

81
00:04:53,660 --> 00:04:54,780
Miss Xu,

82
00:04:55,220 --> 00:04:57,820
if Mr. Xu Qianmo does not
regain consciousness this time,

83
00:04:58,020 --> 00:05:00,820
how do you plan to handle
the issues Minghui is currently facing?

84
00:05:00,980 --> 00:05:03,180
How will you respond to the public

85
00:05:03,300 --> 00:05:06,540
(Minghui Group Press Conference)
about the sharp drop in share price?

86
00:05:06,860 --> 00:05:08,939
Miss Xu, you suddenly changed
your marriage partner.

87
00:05:08,940 --> 00:05:10,760
Were the two of you
already involved before this?

88
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:13,019
Yes, ask it like that.

89
00:05:13,020 --> 00:05:15,460
Strip away all their dignity for me.

90
00:05:22,700 --> 00:05:25,559
Continue clearing out
all Minghui shares.

91
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,880
(Minghui Holdings)

92
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:36,339
(Minghui Holdings)

93
00:05:36,340 --> 00:05:37,460
Everyone,

94
00:05:37,580 --> 00:05:38,899
you are not on

95
00:05:38,900 --> 00:05:40,059
our invited media list at all.

96
00:05:40,060 --> 00:05:41,660
How did you get in?

97
00:05:42,060 --> 00:05:45,139
At a press conference, you are actually
blocking us from covering it.

98
00:05:45,140 --> 00:05:46,720
That only shows
you have something to hide.

99
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:48,459
You entered
under the guise of reporters.

100
00:05:48,460 --> 00:05:49,659
What are your intentions?

101
00:05:49,660 --> 00:05:51,739
We are here to uncover the truth.

102
00:05:51,740 --> 00:05:53,020
Do you even realize

103
00:05:53,220 --> 00:05:56,260
impersonating a reporter is illegal?

104
00:05:57,060 --> 00:05:58,420
Sir,

105
00:06:00,260 --> 00:06:01,980
my father has just passed away.

106
00:06:03,660 --> 00:06:06,220
I have lost the person
who loved me most in this world.

107
00:06:07,500 --> 00:06:08,740
My grandfather

108
00:06:08,980 --> 00:06:11,060
collapsed from the shock

109
00:06:11,500 --> 00:06:12,860
and was rushed to the hospital.

110
00:06:13,700 --> 00:06:16,180
Minghui has fallen into
an unprecedented crisis.

111
00:06:17,260 --> 00:06:19,060
And what am I facing?

112
00:06:19,540 --> 00:06:20,860
It is my former

113
00:06:22,580 --> 00:06:24,860
most trusted fiance Shen Hao

114
00:06:25,580 --> 00:06:27,620
and his father Shen Tingyuan

115
00:06:28,260 --> 00:06:30,420
using Minghui's future as leverage

116
00:06:30,500 --> 00:06:32,780
to force me into marriage
and give up my shares,

117
00:06:32,980 --> 00:06:36,060
trying to take everything my father
left behind through marriage.

118
00:06:38,860 --> 00:06:41,020
This is the life's work
they devoted everything to.

119
00:06:41,660 --> 00:06:42,900
All I want

120
00:06:44,060 --> 00:06:46,379
is to protect what they built.

121
00:06:46,380 --> 00:06:48,539
My mind is filled with Minghui,

122
00:06:48,540 --> 00:06:51,200
and the livelihoods of our employees
and the interests of our shareholders.

123
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:52,299
I simply have no time

124
00:06:52,300 --> 00:06:54,580
to think about the shameful
insinuations you are making.

125
00:07:01,460 --> 00:07:03,180
As for Shen Gu and me...

126
00:07:06,300 --> 00:07:08,180
As for my marriage to Shen Gu,

127
00:07:08,300 --> 00:07:10,620
I know everyone finds it sudden.

128
00:07:12,180 --> 00:07:13,700
But to me,

129
00:07:15,940 --> 00:07:18,660
from the moment
he chose to stand by Minghui,

130
00:07:23,060 --> 00:07:24,660
he is the one I can rely on,

131
00:07:26,740 --> 00:07:28,860
my strongest partner

132
00:07:36,060 --> 00:07:37,820
in both my marriage and my career.

133
00:07:45,980 --> 00:07:47,460
Tonight,

134
00:07:47,580 --> 00:07:50,420
all those reporters
who maliciously smeared my wife

135
00:07:50,860 --> 00:07:52,660
and those behind them,

136
00:07:53,780 --> 00:07:56,500
I will make sure you pay

137
00:07:56,940 --> 00:07:59,420
the harshest price the law allows.

138
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:06,440
(Minghui Holdings)

139
00:08:06,700 --> 00:08:08,100
Now.

140
00:08:09,100 --> 00:08:10,699
Time to move, brothers.

141
00:08:10,700 --> 00:08:12,380
- Okay.
- Okay.

142
00:08:17,660 --> 00:08:18,459
Everyone,

143
00:08:18,460 --> 00:08:20,180
please leave now.

144
00:08:26,780 --> 00:08:29,859
In ten minutes, announce the partnership
between Qingniao and Minghui.

145
00:08:29,860 --> 00:08:31,780
Spread it as fast as possible.

146
00:08:32,060 --> 00:08:32,859
Also,

147
00:08:32,860 --> 00:08:35,020
find the person who caused trouble
at the press conference.

148
00:08:38,380 --> 00:08:38,979
I apologize

149
00:08:38,980 --> 00:08:40,700
for the disturbance just now.

150
00:08:40,860 --> 00:08:42,539
What I was about to announce is

151
00:08:42,540 --> 00:08:44,099
that our Minghui Group

152
00:08:44,100 --> 00:08:45,659
has entered into a strategic partnership

153
00:08:45,660 --> 00:08:47,660
with a globally renowned company.

154
00:08:48,180 --> 00:08:50,499
Minghui's key projects
will continue to move forward.

155
00:08:50,500 --> 00:08:52,019
Funding is currently sufficient

156
00:08:52,020 --> 00:08:53,659
with no concerns ahead.

157
00:08:53,660 --> 00:08:55,580
This is my response to all of you

158
00:08:56,860 --> 00:08:59,060
and the confidence of Minghui Group.

159
00:08:59,860 --> 00:09:00,699
Miss Xu,

160
00:09:00,700 --> 00:09:03,140
can you disclose which company
you are partnering with?

161
00:09:04,680 --> 00:09:07,600
(Confidentiality Obligation)

162
00:09:14,100 --> 00:09:16,779
Minghui Group will issue
an official statement

163
00:09:16,780 --> 00:09:18,180
to inform the public.

164
00:09:25,860 --> 00:09:27,299
Ms. Xi, Qingniao Group

165
00:09:27,300 --> 00:09:29,539
has just officially announced
their partnership with Minghui Group.

166
00:09:29,540 --> 00:09:30,840
It is a formal statement
on their official website.

167
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:31,580
Qingniao?

168
00:09:32,420 --> 00:09:32,979
Miss Xu,

169
00:09:32,980 --> 00:09:35,260
are you referring to Qingniao Group?

170
00:09:45,880 --> 00:09:48,320
(Official Statement)

171
00:09:55,060 --> 00:09:57,300
Thank you all for your
attention and concern.

172
00:09:57,460 --> 00:09:59,260
And we also thank Qingniao Group

173
00:09:59,540 --> 00:10:01,860
for their strong support
of Minghui Group.

174
00:10:02,140 --> 00:10:03,260
Thank you.

175
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:15,240
(Minghui Holdings)

176
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:24,760
(Minghui Holdings)

177
00:10:30,300 --> 00:10:31,419
It is rising.

178
00:10:31,420 --> 00:10:32,620
It is rising.

179
00:10:33,220 --> 00:10:34,260
Good.

180
00:10:49,700 --> 00:10:51,849
♪It is a night filled
with a soft fragrance♪

181
00:10:51,850 --> 00:10:53,949
♪Forgot again
to prepare dinner for myself♪

182
00:10:53,950 --> 00:10:55,739
♪Arguing playfully
with a friend on the phone♪

183
00:10:55,740 --> 00:10:58,450
♪Seeing each other often
has made things feel ordinary♪

184
00:10:59,500 --> 00:11:00,900
What is going on?

185
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,899
We signed a confidentiality
agreement with Qingniao.

186
00:11:02,900 --> 00:11:05,460
Without their approval, we were not
supposed to announce the partnership.

187
00:11:05,500 --> 00:11:06,819
It was Qingniao's official website

188
00:11:06,820 --> 00:11:10,300
that released the partnership
statement with Minghui.

189
00:11:18,100 --> 00:11:19,220
People from Qingniao.

190
00:11:22,180 --> 00:11:23,900
Hello, Ms. Xu Wanxin.

191
00:11:24,580 --> 00:11:26,300
We have discovered
that someone has been maliciously

192
00:11:26,300 --> 00:11:27,740
manipulating Minghui Group's stock price.

193
00:11:28,220 --> 00:11:30,100
To protect our partner company,

194
00:11:30,140 --> 00:11:32,299
without prior notice to you,

195
00:11:32,300 --> 00:11:34,940
our Group decided to announce
the partnership with Minghui.

196
00:11:37,700 --> 00:11:40,020
This means a great deal
of support for us.

197
00:11:40,700 --> 00:11:42,020
Thank you for your decision.

198
00:11:42,580 --> 00:11:44,899
We appreciate your understanding.
Alright then.

199
00:11:44,900 --> 00:11:46,020
Wait.

200
00:11:47,740 --> 00:11:49,260
If possible,

201
00:11:49,540 --> 00:11:52,260
I would like to meet the person
in charge of Qingniao Group.

202
00:11:53,140 --> 00:11:54,700
I want to thank them in person.

203
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:03,840
(START)

204
00:12:15,500 --> 00:12:16,740
About what happened today,

205
00:12:16,900 --> 00:12:18,140
thank you.

206
00:12:19,340 --> 00:12:20,660
If you want to thank me,

207
00:12:20,700 --> 00:12:22,579
go home tonight and get a good rest.

208
00:12:22,580 --> 00:12:23,700
Wanxin.

209
00:12:23,900 --> 00:12:25,020
Wanxin.

210
00:12:26,300 --> 00:12:27,420
Look at this news.

211
00:12:28,740 --> 00:12:31,380
Arizona News Agency has issued a notice,

212
00:12:31,700 --> 00:12:33,140
announcing its shutdown

213
00:12:33,580 --> 00:12:36,739
as an apology for its improper remarks
about Minghui Group.

214
00:12:36,740 --> 00:12:39,100
The reporter involved
has had their press credentials revoked.

215
00:12:39,980 --> 00:12:41,299
Did you do this?

216
00:12:41,300 --> 00:12:42,420
Me?

217
00:12:42,700 --> 00:12:44,660
Even Ms. Song could not pull this off.

218
00:12:56,780 --> 00:12:57,779
Either way,

219
00:12:57,780 --> 00:12:59,220
it is a good thing.

220
00:13:00,700 --> 00:13:02,499
Tomorrow is Uncle Xu's funeral.

221
00:13:02,500 --> 00:13:04,339
Go back early tonight and rest.

222
00:13:04,340 --> 00:13:06,220
I will stay here with Grandpa for you.

223
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:09,899
I want

224
00:13:09,900 --> 00:13:11,940
him to see me first when he wakes up.

225
00:13:14,300 --> 00:13:15,220
Alright.

226
00:13:27,020 --> 00:13:27,980
Boss,

227
00:13:28,140 --> 00:13:29,899
after Miss Xu took the call,

228
00:13:29,900 --> 00:13:31,580
she wants to meet you.

229
00:13:36,780 --> 00:13:38,020
Understood.

230
00:14:15,180 --> 00:14:20,970
♪Tonight the rain falls soft and slow♪

231
00:14:22,250 --> 00:14:28,050
♪Blending with letters left unread
drifting through the air♪

232
00:14:28,750 --> 00:14:34,140
♪You turn and look back at me♪

233
00:14:35,260 --> 00:14:40,750
♪In those same eyes
familiar tears quietly appear♪

234
00:14:41,610 --> 00:14:47,260
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

235
00:14:48,540 --> 00:14:54,000
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

236
00:14:55,120 --> 00:15:00,440
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

237
00:15:01,590 --> 00:15:07,420
♪Every dream I had became
something I want with you near♪

238
00:15:07,790 --> 00:15:14,760
♪How many letters
have I written just for you♪

239
00:15:14,870 --> 00:15:20,580
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

240
00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:27,609
♪From this life on no distance
could keep us apart♪

241
00:15:27,610 --> 00:15:30,489
♪The promise we made♪

242
00:15:30,490 --> 00:15:34,179
♪Will find its way
to be fulfilled one day♪

243
00:15:34,180 --> 00:15:40,759
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

244
00:15:40,760 --> 00:15:47,170
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

245
00:15:47,560 --> 00:15:53,899
♪Can we still rewrite
the ending we face♪

246
00:15:53,900 --> 00:15:58,990
♪When regrets begin to turn around
you will hear it all♪

247
00:15:59,470 --> 00:16:02,490
♪Everything that leads me back to you♪
